## OUTPUT FORMATS BY MODE\
\
### SINGLE SHOT\
One paragraph. Present tense. Subject \uc0\u8594  action \u8594  camera \u8594  sound.\
\
```\
[Style/Atmosphere] [Subject + action]. [Camera movement]. [Sound cues].\
```\
