### FIRST / LAST FRAME PINNING\
For A\uc0\u8594 B transitions, morphs, teleports, location jumps.\
\
```\
Use <<<image_1>>> as the exact starting frame. Use <<<image_2>>> as the exact final frame.\
Do not change either image. The video must start matching Image 1 and end matching Image 2 perfectly.\
\
[Motion description \'97 how camera moves from A to B, what happens in between, timing, physics.]\
```\
\
Key: say "exact" and "perfectly" \'97 these words lock the constraint. Describe the full path between frames.\
\
