\
### TRANSFORMATION SEQUENCE\
Vehicle/object \uc0\u8594  creature/robot. Second-marked beats.\
\
```\
[Object] is [location]. The [object] begins to violently disassemble and reorganize, transforming into [creature/robot description].\
\
[00\'9602s: The Setup]\
[Wide shot, eye-level]. [Object] [action] in [environment]. Tone is grounded and realistic.\
\
[02\'9605s: Transformation Begins]\
[Dynamic VFX action shot]. The [object] violently bursts open. [Specific body parts emerge \'97 head, eyes, material].\
[Chassis/panels fold, spin, reconfigure into limbs].\
\
[05\'9608s: The Ejection]\
[Fast-paced tracking shot]. [Driver/occupant ejected]. [Machine completes transformation]. [Environmental reaction \'97 dust, debris].\
\
[08\'9611s: The Mount]\
[Action shot]. [Human response \'97 charges, vaults, lands on creature].\
\
[11\'9614s: The Hero Pose]\
[Low angle, epic]. [Human + creature stance]. [Creature aggression \'97 jaws open, roar]. [Lens flare, scale reveal].\
```\
\
Key: ground the opening in realism before breaking physics. Name specific body parts as they emerge. End on low-angle hero pose with lens flare.\
